{"id":175,"idInBook":2572,"chapterId":10,"bookId":14,"arabic":"وَعَنِ ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ قَالَ: احْتَجَمَ النَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ وَهُوَ محرم","english":{"narrator":"","text":"Ibn ‘Abbas said that the Prophet had himself cupped when he was in the sacred state.\n\nBukhari and Muslim."},"hadithNumber":2572,"hadithId":175,"reference":"10:175","meta":{"id":"mishkat_almasabih","length":4428,"totalChapters":25,"arabic":{"title":"مشكاة المصابيح","author":"الإمام الكاتب التبريزي"},"english":{"title":"Mishkat Al Masabih","author":"Al-Khatib Al-Tabrizi"}},"chapter":{"id":10,"bookId":14,"arabic":"كتاب المناسك","english":"The Rites of Pilgrimage","startHadith":2398,"endHadith":2643,"totalHadiths":246},"version":{"name":"mishkat_almasabih","title":"Mishkat Al Masabih","chapters":25}}